=Description=

Jessica Conrad:

"In what may at first seem an unlikely partnership, choreographer Daria Fain and architect/poet Robert Kocik have been working together since the late 80s to create an ongoing series of presentations devoted to reunifying language, our bodies, and the environment. Central to their work is a commitment to advancing the common good, and a practice called “commoning,” through their Commons Choir."
(http://onthecommons.org/commons-choir-revealing-history-commons-through-song-and-dance)


